Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.14,0:00:02.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Pain that won’t heal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.16,0:00:03.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sadness you feel
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.98,0:00:06.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Scars that just refuse to fade\Nfrom memory
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.20,0:00:09.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sometimes the burden’s too much\Nfor one to bear
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.05,0:00:12.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t give up on me,\Nplease don’t turn me away
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.52,0:00:14.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.92,0:00:18.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I’ll hold your hand in mine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.70,0:00:25.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Will I lose my hold on her someday?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.93,0:00:32.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Will her smile fade in a flood of tears\NOr can I keep the fears at bay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.44,0:00:37.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Echoing, distant voices wither into silence.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.07,0:00:41.71,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But there is one thing that\Nwill never ever age…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.48,0:00:46.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My love for you is timeless
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.89,0:00:47.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Pain that won’t heal
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.85,0:00:49.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sadness you feel
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.64,0:00:51.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Smiles with hearts’ bitterness replaced
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.79,0:00:53.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,“I’ll never smile again”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.30,0:00:54.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,“I’ll never let love in”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.96,0:00:57.45,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don’t ever say such things to me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.45,0:01:00.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A future we cannot see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.64,0:01:03.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All happenings\NFind meaning in the story
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.32,0:01:08.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In time the clouds will clear away,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.14,0:01:12.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,so just stay, please stay with me…\NWhoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.20,0:01:17.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who are we to pass through you?\NWhoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.39,0:01:20.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That answer will find you someday
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.40,0:01:53.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.29,0:02:02.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Ichigo! Answer! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.98,0:02:19.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's coming!\NThree…maybe more.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.46,0:02:20.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let's retreat for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.80,0:02:22.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let them find us.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.12,0:02:24.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.98,0:02:42.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.03,0:02:43.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Abarai!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.37,0:02:47.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Abarai!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.37,0:02:49.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?! Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.31,0:02:53.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be… Abarai can't have lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.28,0:02:57.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,His opponent seems to\Nhave gotten away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.49,0:02:58.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we give chase?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.46,0:03:03.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, first we must get Abarai treated.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.04,0:03:05.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Get a stretcher.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.48,0:03:07.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We're taking him back\Nto the barracks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.04,0:03:13.53,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Healing power?\NWithout using any medicine?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.92,0:03:16.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's different with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.88,0:03:20.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With other Soul Reapers,\Ntheir spiritual power is mostly for combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.41,0:03:24.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But those of us in Squad 4\Nhave healing power as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.35,0:03:31.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Although…\Nthat's about all we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.39,0:03:37.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see… And…?\NHow is Ichigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.17,0:03:42.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's very bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.05,0:03:45.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He took direct hits from\Na Zanpaku-to of a Lieutenant…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.92,0:03:47.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's to be expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.68,0:03:49.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, he'd have died instantly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:51.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He has an unbelievable will to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.08,0:03:58.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll heal him without fail.\NPlease give me some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.20,0:04:01.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll heal him in one night.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.54,0:04:04.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's…!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.18,0:04:08.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When I found him,\Nhe was already in this condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.54,0:04:13.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If only I'd found him sooner\Nand assisted his fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.43,0:04:17.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't blame yourself, Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.67,0:04:23.03,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,In any case,\NI'll contact Squad 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.52,0:04:25.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll ask for emergency relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.54,0:04:28.20,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.58,0:04:34.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Kuchiki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.43,0:04:36.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Put him in prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.85,0:04:41.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,B-But… Abarai fought Ryoka by himself.\NAnd yet…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.85,0:04:43.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No excuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.92,0:04:49.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If he entered a fight alone,\Ndefeat is absolutely forbidden.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.91,0:04:52.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I have no use for a fool who\Ndid not understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.25,0:04:56.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He is an eyesore.\NTake him away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.53,0:05:02.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please wait! How can you say…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.84,0:05:04.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Lieutenant Abarai…\N– Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.85,0:05:06.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.72,0:05:11.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My deepest apologies!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.52,0:05:17.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My deepest apologies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.36,0:05:33.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hinamori, let's follow his orders,\Nand take Abarai to prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.53,0:05:35.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But…!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.18,0:05:36.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.78,0:05:39.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Ichimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.80,0:05:43.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why'd he have to talk like that…huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.92,0:05:47.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's as scary as ever…\Nthe Captain of Squad 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.14,0:05:54.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, don't worry.\NI'll call Squad 4.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.88,0:05:56.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.90,0:06:00.56,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. Come with me, Izuru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.87,0:06:01.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.19,0:06:04.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.14,0:06:12.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, Abarai got messed up\Npretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.84,0:06:14.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hitsugaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.17,0:06:16.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey… I'm a Captain, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.80,0:06:18.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And you're gonna address me\Nlike that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.68,0:06:19.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Never mind that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.39,0:06:23.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How come all you Captains\Ncreep around so silently?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.05,0:06:25.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And why are you\Nhere anyway, Hitsugaya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.67,0:06:30.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes…why are you here?\NWithout your Lieutenant?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.75,0:06:33.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I came to warn you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.38,0:06:34.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Warn?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:38.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful of Squad 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.03,0:06:42.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Squad 3? You mean, Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.43,0:06:45.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I mean Ichimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.16,0:06:47.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not sure about Kira, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.69,0:06:51.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The alarm sounds quite\Nconveniently these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.91,0:06:58.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand…\Njust what you mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.34,0:07:02.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And you think you\Ncan get away with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.89,0:07:07.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You should not underestimate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.07,0:07:16.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, it won't hurt to be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.46,0:07:20.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Especially…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.33,0:07:30.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The situation…is critical.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.88,0:07:34.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This means that we are\Nshort one Lieutenant
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.00,0:07:35.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,in the Thirteen Court Guard Squads.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.64,0:07:41.76,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We can no longer leave this\Nto the lower-ranked members.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.24,0:07:44.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, in view of the situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.22,0:07:48.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I will not discipline…\NIchimaru for his independent actions earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.86,0:07:51.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.76,0:07:55.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, I will allow senior officers,\Nincluding Lieutenants,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.04,0:07:58.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,to carry their Zanpaku-to at all times
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.27,0:08:01.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,as well as allow full release of their\NZanpaku-to in the Court, as in wartime.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.37,0:08:05.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Carry the Zanpaku-to all the time, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.23,0:08:10.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Full release as in wartime, huh?\NI con’t be happier.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.15,0:08:16.09,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If someone hadn't allowed\NRyoka to escape,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.09,0:08:17.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,we wouldn't be talking about this now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.28,0:08:20.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, stop that talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.14,0:08:25.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, 'cuz he'll be my prey from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.14,0:08:32.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Men…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.65,0:08:37.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is all-out war.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.53,0:08:58.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're awake, Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.70,0:09:02.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hanataro…I…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.77,0:09:07.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't move.\NYour wounds haven't closed yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.52,0:09:08.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wounds?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.10,0:09:13.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh right…I fought Renji…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.32,0:09:16.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.88,0:09:21.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Hanataro. I'll be fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.18,0:09:23.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?\NYou can't get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.24,0:09:26.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chad and the others\Ndon't know where Rukia is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.16,0:09:28.39,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I must go and…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.64,0:09:31.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo! You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.89,0:09:36.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You see? You're not recovered yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.44,0:09:40.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you go out in your condition,\Nyou're certain to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.12,0:09:42.35,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.96,0:09:53.88,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If I can knock him out like that,\Nhow can he be all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.88,0:09:56.84,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Sleep until you're healed, idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.84,0:10:01.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ganju! Oh no…\Nhe's got another wound now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.03,0:10:05.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're so rough, Ganju.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.77,0:10:08.70,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! I stopped him, didn't I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.70,0:10:10.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't complain about how I did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.68,0:10:13.05,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.12,0:10:16.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think that the slash across\Nhis left shoulder and chest
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.38,0:10:18.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,would be this shallow.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.85,0:10:21.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it would definitely\Nbe a fatal wound…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.48,0:10:26.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Was it because of…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.30,0:10:28.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,that mask inside his clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:53.60,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,To be able to stop\NLieutenant Abarai's slash…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.99,0:10:57.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what it is? And…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.14,0:11:01.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This mask looks too much\Nlike a Hollow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:04.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it, Ichigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.65,0:11:12.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.50,0:11:14.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.63,0:11:19.16,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Can you tell me\Nwhat's going on outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.16,0:11:20.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just a little is fine…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.86,0:11:26.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know\Nthe details either.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.38,0:11:30.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But we've heard that\NLieutenant Abarai was taken down.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.36,0:11:32.33,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Renji?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.99,0:11:55.85,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done treating Lieutenant Abarai's\Nwounds for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.55,0:11:57.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.23,0:12:13.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Abarai…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.25,0:12:22.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you attack the Ryoka alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.28,0:12:25.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Does it have anything to do\Nwith Rukia?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.52,0:12:51.47,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Owwee! You!\NYou don't have to get so serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.47,0:12:54.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We can't afford to get\Nhurt practicing, you know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.40,0:12:58.41,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid! Unless we're serious,\Npracticing is useless.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.41,0:13:00.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You just didn't pay attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.95,0:13:03.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll be your opponent, next.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.14,0:13:05.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Kira…!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.43,0:13:08.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's no fun beating a girl, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.61,0:13:09.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying, Kira?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.90,0:13:11.63,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you making fun of women?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.63,0:13:14.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no…nothing like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.08,0:13:16.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Quit acting so embarrassed!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.56,0:13:21.07,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I wasn't thinking of\Nyou as an opponent,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.07,0:13:23.21,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but at least I won't be bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.00,0:13:27.18,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you eat your words.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.28,0:13:45.90,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're good, Abarai!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:50.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So are you! You've improved, Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.64,0:13:56.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Kira, just a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.68,0:13:58.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Rukia!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.98,0:14:01.23,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Abarai!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.43,0:14:14.73,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Abarai…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.11,0:14:22.38,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Lieutenant Hinamori! Special wartime\Norders were just announced.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:24.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Special wartime orders?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.35,0:14:27.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Special wartime orders!\N– Special wartime orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.52,0:14:29.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Special wartime orders!\N– Special wartime orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.33,0:14:32.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.04,0:14:35.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,First: All senior officers\Nincluding Lieutenants
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.74,0:14:39.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,will be permitted to\Nwear their swords at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.49,0:14:44.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Second: They will be permitted to\Nrelease their Zanpaku-to as in wartime.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.30,0:14:47.13,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Those are the orders from
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.13,0:14:50.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Squad 1 Captain and Captain General of\Nthe 13 Court Guard Squads
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.78,0:14:52.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shigekuni Genryusai Yamamoto.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.78,0:14:54.78,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.13,0:15:05.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wartime orders.\NPermission to wear swords…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.24,0:15:08.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why did it come to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.60,0:15:14.68,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,They don't have to let us carry Zanpaku-to.\NPeace is all that I want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.76,0:15:20.77,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And…Hitsugaya's warning…\NI'm worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.78,0:15:24.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful of Squad 3…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.51,0:15:26.22,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Especially…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.02,0:15:30.30,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Aizen…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.62,0:15:45.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?\NIs something wrong, Hinamori?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.46,0:15:48.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.28,0:15:54.50,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What is it at this hour?\NDawn is about to break.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.95,0:15:58.01,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I know full well that\Nthis is very rude…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.01,0:16:00.91,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but may I have a quick word?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.38,0:16:08.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I promise not to make any blunders.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.19,0:16:10.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So please…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.00,0:16:15.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I would turn you\Naway simply for rudeness?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.02,0:16:16.40,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,N-No…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.43,0:16:20.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do I seem so heartless these days?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.72,0:16:23.79,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,N-No…not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.63,0:16:28.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then come inside.\NToday was a very difficult day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.19,0:16:31.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Talk to your heart's content.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.65,0:16:43.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Owweee…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.91,0:16:48.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Are you awake, Ichigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.32,0:16:50.57,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that Ganju!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.11,0:16:53.00,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You remembered?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.00,0:16:55.98,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally! That guy…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.98,0:16:58.46,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,laying his hand on\Nan injured man!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.74,0:17:02.19,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm glad Ganju was able to\Nstop you earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.66,0:17:04.43,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, you would have\Nstarted to bleed again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.92,0:17:08.97,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I know… I gotta cool my head, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.91,0:17:12.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's better if you lie down for a bit longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.00,0:17:16.74,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No one will come after you here.\NSo rest assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.14,0:17:22.96,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder what happened to him…\Nthat Renji?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.96,0:17:26.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Oh…\NI'm not really sure of the details…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.25,0:17:29.99,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But he would normally be sent\Nto emergency relief.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.20,0:17:32.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.24,0:17:33.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.09,0:17:46.04,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.41,0:17:49.58,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you have something to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.58,0:17:51.80,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Err, yes… I…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.80,0:17:54.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How is Abarai's condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.00,0:17:58.89,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh… his life isn't in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.24,0:18:00.44,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.99,0:18:04.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about the\Ncaptains' meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.95,0:18:07.36,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Kuchiki asked that\NAbarai be discharged,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.36,0:18:09.48,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,but there were objections\Nand so he backed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.89,0:18:11.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Once his wounds heal,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.08,0:18:13.29,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,he'll be able to return\Nto his squad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.83,0:18:17.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,By chance, were you the\None who objected, Captain Aizen?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.80,0:18:23.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Not only me. He's an excellent officer\Nand liked by everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.86,0:18:26.27,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's not one person in\Nthe Thirteen Court Guard Squads
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.27,0:18:29.12,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,who would rejoice at his dismissal.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.73,0:18:30.65,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.47,0:18:38.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Aizen…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.08,0:18:39.75,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.27,0:18:46.37,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I won't disturb you…\NSo may I sit here and watch you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.01,0:18:48.66,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Or is it an imposition?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.12,0:18:52.52,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No, I don't mind.\NStay as long as you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.49,0:18:54.31,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.74,0:19:30.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Darn!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.08,0:19:32.94,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! I…I fell asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.38,0:19:34.24,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.56,0:19:43.02,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! Look at the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.59,0:19:52.82,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, I wish the Captain\Nwould've waken me up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.82,0:19:55.42,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if I'll make it\Nto the meeting on time…?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.92,0:20:11.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take a shortcut…!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.51,0:20:27.06,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There, I think I made it…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.29,0:20:46.08,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What was that scream?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.08,0:20:47.86,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It came from the Eastern Wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.86,0:20:50.62,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That was Hinamori's voice…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.53,0:20:54.49,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hinamori!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.49,0:20:58.61,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hinamori! What's wrong? Hinamori!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.17,0:21:08.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Whaa--?! I-It can't be…!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.85,0:21:12.14,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Aizen!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.00,0:21:20.17,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Captain Aizen!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.10,0:21:41.64,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I looked up into the night sky\Nand saw a comet
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.64,0:21:48.92,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see you right now,\Nbut I can't fly
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.92,0:21:56.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If I could become a comet
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.25,0:22:01.25,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I would fly across the sky… I'm sure
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.25,0:22:08.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I would circle the skies and shine over you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.81,0:22:13.67,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,With this instantaneous light\Nthat will definitely reach you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.67,0:22:21.15,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If I could become a comet
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.15,0:22:24.81,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I'll always stay close to you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.81,0:22:26.95,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now and forever
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.07,0:22:35.59,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Hanataro.\NI'm fully recovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.59,0:22:38.26,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's about the only thing I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.26,0:22:40.32,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,As long as we have Hanataro,\Nyou're fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.32,0:22:42.54,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,So Ichigo, go and get all cut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.54,0:22:44.10,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Absolutely not!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.10,0:22:46.28,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,– Go for it! Just go!\N– No thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.28,0:22:47.83,Default,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Just get cut up!